🚀 Exciting News! 🚀  
We're hosting a Gen AI Hackathon & Workshop at our college on March 1st!  

Join us to learn how to create a full-stack web application using Gen AI. 🌐✨  
This workshop isn't just about learning; it's about innovating. 💡  

Participants will have the opportunity to showcase their skills in a hackathon, and the best web application will earn a chance to attend the Mumbai Tech Fest! 🎉  

Are you ready to unleash your creativity and take your skills to the next level?  
Comment below if you're in! 👇💬
